The electronic ledger is a text-based software (Runs in the Terminal).
The electronic ledger display the basic description of the cyrptocurrency selected.
The electronic ledger allows to enter, withdraw and record transactions.
The electronic ledger shows the past transaction records (deposit, withdrawal, etc) in tables or graphs. 
The electronic ledger shows the real time conversion rates from the cryptocurrency to other major currencies in the world (yen, usd, eur). 
The electronic ledger has an address book to make it more convenient to send money and reduce errors when typing in address manually (edit and delete).
